      <title>迪拜不再只是中转枢纽，而是寻求更多回头客</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/a-transfer-hub-no-more-dubai-seeks-to-win-more-return-visitors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜正在寻求增加航空运力，并计划推出一种方便回程的新签证来吸引更多游客，因为它正将其重点从作为中转枢纽和短期目的地转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/a-transfer-hub-no-more-dubai-seeks-to-win-more-return-visitors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 05:38:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前英国央行副行长称瑞士“大而不倒”计划存在缺陷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/switzerland-s-too-big-to-fail-plan-is-flawed-ex-boe-deputy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位全球金融规则的主要制定者表示，瑞士对瑞银集团等全球系统性银行的清算方式，在某些方面可能会加剧未来假设性危机中的混乱局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/switzerland-s-too-big-to-fail-plan-is-flawed-ex-boe-deputy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 05:34:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究警告称，美国银行存在商业地产盲点风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/us-banks-have-a-commercial-property-blind-spot-risk-study-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新研究表明，由于美国大型银行向房地产投资信托提供了信贷额度和定期贷款，它们在商业地产方面的风险敞口可能比监管机构认为的要大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/us-banks-have-a-commercial-property-blind-spot-risk-study-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列预计还需要七个月的战斗才能击败哈马斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-30/israel-sees-seven-more-months-of-fighting-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国家安全顾问表示，以色列可能无法在年底前击败哈马斯，这凸显了该国在实现其消灭加沙伊斯兰组织的既定目标方面面临的困难。控制风险副主任 Niamh McBurney 与 Joumanna Bercetche 就“中东和非洲视野”进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-30/israel-sees-seven-more-months-of-fighting-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 05:06:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
